<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:06:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>被哈马斯扣押的法裔以色列人质的母亲：“乞求全世界带我的孩子回家”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-french-israeli-hostage-by-hamas-begging-the-world-to-bring-my-baby-home/0000018b-3d20-d101-a9ab-bf3c37aa0000</link><description>21 岁的玛雅·谢姆 (Maya Schem) 拥有法国和以色列双重国籍，在哈马斯袭击加沙边境附近的以色列社区时被哈马斯抓走。她的家人直到哈马斯在加沙发布她的视频几天后才发现她被扣为人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:48:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-french-israeli-hostage-by-hamas-begging-the-world-to-bring-my-baby-home/0000018b-3d20-d101-a9ab-bf3c37aa0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太白宫官员在访问以色列之前赞扬拜登：“这就是他”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/jewish-white-house-officials-applaud-biden-ahead-of-israel-visit-this-is-who-he-is/0000018b-3d41-d450-a3af-7d5d3f590000</link><description>一名高级工作人员表示，“现在有两件事给了我力量：犹太人民的韧性以及拜登总统的领导力和道德清晰度”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/jewish-white-house-officials-applaud-biden-ahead-of-israel-visit-this-is-who-he-is/0000018b-3d41-d450-a3af-7d5d3f590000</guid></item><item><title>考古、圣经机构谴责哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-17/ty-article/archaeological-biblical-institutions-condemn-hamas-massacre/0000018b-3d42-d101-a9ab-bf7e03f60000</link><description>以色列考古学家抱怨一周以来他们的沉默，美国海外研究协会周一谴责哈马斯对以色列平民的“恶毒屠杀”，而圣经文学协会则对世界反犹太主义抬头表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:15:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-17/ty-article/archaeological-biblical-institutions-condemn-hamas-massacre/0000018b-3d42-d101-a9ab-bf7e03f60000</guid></item><item><title>BBC记者因赞扬哈马斯袭击以色列平民而被停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bbc-reporters-suspended-for-praising-hamas-attacks-on-israeli-civilians/0000018b-3d75-d450-a3af-7d7d8cf80000</link><description>据报道，英国广播公司 (BBC) 旗下频道的一名记者点赞了一些推文，称针对以色列平民的屠杀是“一次高质量的行动”和“一个令人自豪的场景”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:54:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bbc-reporters-suspended-for-praising-hamas-attacks-on-israeli-civilians/0000018b-3d75-d450-a3af-7d7d8cf80000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争以来，澳大利亚犹太社区的宗教间关系紧张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/australian-jewish-communitys-interfaith-relations-strained-since-gaza-war/0000018b-3d14-d101-a9ab-bf3cff230000</link><description>至少两名拉比从澳大利亚犹太穆斯林基督教协会辞职，墨尔本地区犹太社区理事会正在考虑暂停跨宗教接触</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/australian-jewish-communitys-interfaith-relations-strained-since-gaza-war/0000018b-3d14-d101-a9ab-bf3cff230000</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨访问以色列，德国的特殊承诺面临最终考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-scholz-visits-israel-germanys-special-commitment-faces-the-ultimate-test/0000018b-3d23-d07d-a99b-fde3c12f0000</link><description>现在，德国比以往任何时候都更有历史责任积极、坚定不移地保卫以色列，而不仅仅是口头上</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-scholz-visits-israel-germanys-special-commitment-faces-the-ultimate-test/0000018b-3d23-d07d-a99b-fde3c12f0000</guid></item><item><title>“战争爆发，血沸腾”：定居者迫使巴勒斯坦人离开西岸家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theres-war-blood-is-boiling-settlers-force-palestinians-out-their-homes-in-west-bank/0000018b-3d35-d5b8-a78b-fd756b2e0000</link><description>以色列与哈马斯战争期间，约旦河西岸的定居者暴力不断升级：约旦河谷一个村庄的巴勒斯坦居民表示，定居者给了他们五个小时的时间逃离家园</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/theres-war-blood-is-boiling-settlers-force-palestinians-out-their-homes-in-west-bank/0000018b-3d35-d5b8-a78b-fd756b2e0000</guid></item><item><title>由于通往埃及的拉法过境点仍然关闭，加沙人在医院寻求庇护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/as-rafah-border-crossing-to-egypt-remains-closed-gazans-seek-shelter-in-hospitals/0000018b-3cde-d101-a9ab-befe5d430000</link><description>埃及表示，拉法过境点是战斗前的一条重要动脉，现在是运送急需物资的关键路线，该过境点尚未正式关闭，但由于以色列对加沙一侧的空袭而无法通行</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 12:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/as-rafah-border-crossing-to-egypt-remains-closed-gazans-seek-shelter-in-hospitals/0000018b-3cde-d101-a9ab-befe5d430000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯绑架的以色列妇女的父亲：“加沙父母也很痛苦”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/father-of-israeli-woman-abducted-by-hamas-gaza-parents-are-in-pain-too/0000018b-3cf0-d450-a3af-7dfcf27d0000</link><description>“我正在以自己的方式战斗。不是带着愤怒。通过对话，”雅科夫·阿加马尼 (Yakov Argamani) 说道。在超新星音乐节袭击期间，骑摩托车的哈马斯恐怖分子拍摄了一段视频，可以看到他的女儿诺亚 (Noa)。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/father-of-israeli-woman-abducted-by-hamas-gaza-parents-are-in-pain-too/0000018b-3cf0-d450-a3af-7dfcf27d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争的最初几个小时：到底发生了什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-first-hours-of-the-israel-hamas-war-what-actually-took-place/0000018b-38bc-d0ac-a39f-b9be58df0000</link><description>即使在哈马斯对以色列家庭发动凶残袭击 11 天后，事件发生的所有细节仍无法得知。这是目前我们所知道的</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:21:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-first-hours-of-the-israel-hamas-war-what-actually-took-place/0000018b-38bc-d0ac-a39f-b9be58df0000</guid></item><item><title>在恐怖袭击中杀死两名瑞典人的嫌疑枪手在医院死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-17/ty-article/suspected-gunman-who-killed-two-swedes-in-terror-attack-dies-in-hospital/0000018b-3c72-d5b8-a78b-fd73d2bb0000</link><description>此次枪击事件发生之际，欧洲因以色列与哈马斯冲突而引发的安全担忧加剧，不过比利时联邦检察官表示，没有证据表明袭击者与最近以色列和巴勒斯坦武装分子之间重新爆发的冲突有任何联系，但他受到伊斯兰国的启发</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-17/ty-article/suspected-gunman-who-killed-two-swedes-in-terror-attack-dies-in-hospital/0000018b-3c72-d5b8-a78b-fd73d2bb0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯会见内塔尼亚胡新一轮穿梭外交</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/blinken-meets-with-netanyahu-in-new-round-of-shuttle-diplomacy/0000018b-3a31-d5b8-a78b-fb7194b80000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理还与阿拉伯联合酋长国总统谢赫·穆罕默德·本·扎耶德和俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京等多位世界领导人进行了交谈</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 08:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/blinken-meets-with-netanyahu-in-new-round-of-shuttle-diplomacy/0000018b-3a31-d5b8-a78b-fb7194b80000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特负责人：我们无法阻止袭击，责任落在我身上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-chief-we-were-unable-to-thwart-the-attack-responsibility-for-this-falls-on-me/0000018b-39fd-d450-a3af-79fdc6ae0000</link><description>追随以色列国防军参谋长哈勒维和国家安全顾问哈内格比的脚步，罗南·巴尔也对导致 10 月 7 日大屠杀的失败负有责任。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 05:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-chief-we-were-unable-to-thwart-the-attack-responsibility-for-this-falls-on-me/0000018b-39fd-d450-a3af-79fdc6ae0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人在与真主党的冲突中受伤；以色列国防军：为加沙下一阶段做准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-live/biden-set-to-visit-israel-on-wednesday-israeli-army-strikes-more-than-200-hamas-targets/0000018b-3b3b-d450-a3af-7b3f775c0000</link><description>美国国务卿布林肯结束与内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的会晤，拜登总统准备对以色列进行历史性且前所未有的访问。舒尔茨总理准备访问以色列 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯：一夜之间有 49 人被杀，加沙死亡人数超过 2,700 人</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 04:26:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-live/biden-set-to-visit-israel-on-wednesday-israeli-army-strikes-more-than-200-hamas-targets/0000018b-3b3b-d450-a3af-7b3f775c0000</guid></item><item><title>即使以色列镇压哈马斯，新的威胁也会从加沙的废墟中出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/even-if-israel-crushes-hamas-new-threats-will-emerge-from-the-ashes-of-gaza/0000018b-3a2e-dd09-a1bf-3aae84b50000</link><description>即使以色列实现其所有既定目标，如果没有确保加沙地带新秩序的退出计划，目前针对哈马斯的战争也无法结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 03:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/even-if-israel-crushes-hamas-new-threats-will-emerge-from-the-ashes-of-gaza/0000018b-3a2e-dd09-a1bf-3aae84b50000</guid></item><item><title>专注于哈马斯，以色列选择暂时克制真主党的挑衅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/with-focus-fixed-firmly-on-gaza-israel-turns-the-other-cheek-to-hezbollah-provocations/0000018b-3a2c-d0ac-a39f-bb2ee43e0000</link><description>以色列的主要焦点显然是南部战线，因此它似乎愿意在北部战线忍受相当多的痛苦，并满足于与真主党针锋相对 - 而无需动用其全部军事力量</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/with-focus-fixed-firmly-on-gaza-israel-turns-the-other-cheek-to-hezbollah-provocations/0000018b-3a2c-d0ac-a39f-bb2ee43e0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-3b6e-d101-a9ab-bb7e3c0e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 02:21:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-3b6e-d101-a9ab-bb7e3c0e0000</guid></item><item><title>83 岁的 Um Fayez 阿姨再次被告知要南迁。这次她拒绝了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/aunt-um-fayez-83-is-again-told-to-move-south-this-time-she-refuses/0000018b-3a2f-d450-a3af-7b3fdd160000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:33:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/aunt-um-fayez-83-is-again-told-to-move-south-this-time-she-refuses/0000018b-3a2f-d450-a3af-7b3fdd160000</guid></item><item><title>拜登将于周三对以色列进行史无前例的访问，以表示“坚定不移的支持”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-make-unprecedented-visit-to-israel-on-wednesday-to-show-unshakable-support/0000018b-3afb-d101-a9ab-baff72200000</link><description>在特拉维夫举行数小时会谈后，美国高级外交官布林肯表示，美国总统将与以色列领导人就哈马斯扣押的人质和加沙的人道主义危机进行直接交谈</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-make-unprecedented-visit-to-israel-on-wednesday-to-show-unshakable-support/0000018b-3afb-d101-a9ab-baff72200000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战斗进入第11天，以色列从黎巴嫩边境撤离公民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/israel-evacuates-citizens-from-lebanon-border-as-gaza-fighting-enters-11th-day/0000018b-3a30-dd09-a1bf-3ab8ba8c0000</link><description>联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构否认自称与加沙卫生部有联系的人没收用于人道主义目的的燃料和医疗设备的声明</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 23:36:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/israel-evacuates-citizens-from-lebanon-border-as-gaza-fighting-enters-11th-day/0000018b-3a30-dd09-a1bf-3ab8ba8c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>